# Auth errors
E2000 = The account does not exist. Enter a different email or username.
E2001 = The password is incorrect. Try again.
E2002 = Your account is temporarily locked due to too many failed sign-in attempts. Try again later.
E2003 = Your account has been disabled. Contact your administrator.
E2004 = Your sign-in session has expired. Please start over.
E2005 = Invalid sign-in state. Please start over.
E2006 =
    { $credential_type ->
        [password] Password sign-in is not available for this account.
        [otp] Verification code sign-in is not available for this account.
       *[other] This sign-in method is not supported.
    }
E2007 = The verification code is incorrect. Try again.
E2008 = Too many failed attempts. Please try again later.
E2009 = The session { $session_id } does not exist.
E2010 = Your session has expired. Please sign in again.
E2011 = Your session has been revoked. Please sign in again.
